casebody.data:
No. 444,

October Term, 1956.

Tatko Brothers Slate Co., Inc., v. Vermont Structural Slate Co., Inc. W. Brown Morton, Jr., Maxwell E. Sparrow and J. Preston Swecker for movant-petitioner. John C. Blair and Richard P. Schulze for respondent in opposition.

The motion to recall order denying certiorari, 352 U. S. 917, and to enter order granting certiorari and summarily vacating the judgment of the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit and remanding to that court for reconsideration is denied.
